<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='156:182'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0084', 'WYG', '112-1a' );" name="112-1a" class="pb">[112-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='182:190'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='190:200'>　禮書卷一百十三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='200:221'>　　　　　　　　　　　　宋　陳祥道　撰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='221:247'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0084', 'WYG', '112-2a' );" name="112-2a" class="pb">[112-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
