<p><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='277:303'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0084', 'WYG', '112-4a' );" name="112-4a" class="pb">[112-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
